Detailed Description

SmsSentProvider is the provider to retrieve the already sent sms from the sim. An instance of this class is part of the Apoxi Data Control. A pointer to this provider can be retrieved from the main provider via the id:

c_sms_sent_provider_id

Please refer to SmsProvider for possible columns

NOTE: Please do not instantiate this class.
